---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Install" prose>
  <h1>Install</h1>
  <p>
    Hexpunk ships as <code>@hexpunk/core</code> on npm. Install alongside <code>lit</code>:
  </p>

  <pre><code>bun add @hexpunk/core lit</code></pre>

  <p>
    Then import the elements you want (or the full barrel for everything):
  </p>

  <pre><code>import "@hexpunk/core";</code></pre>

  <p>
    The package side-effects-registers every <code>&lt;hp-*&gt;</code> tag via Lit's
    <code>@customElement</code> decorator on import.
  </p>

  <h2>Tokens</h2>
  <p>
    The dark-theme token set ships as <code>@hexpunk/core/tokens.dark.css</code>. Link or import it
    once at the app root.
  </p>
</Layout>
